--------

**workspace status**

::

    Workspace not installed

    Workspace requirements: C:\git\tools\python_workspace\requirements.txt
    Workspace path: C:\git\tools\python_workspace\workspace_env37
    Workspace scripts: C:\git\tools\python_workspace\workspace_env37\bin

